#: ../src/iop/diffuse.c:1835
msgctxt "section"
msgid "direction"
msgstr "ທິດທາງ"

#: ../src/iop/diffuse.c:1841
msgid ""
"direction of 1st order speed (set above).\n"
"\n"
"negative values follow gradients more closely, \n"
"positive values rather avoid edges (isophotes), \n"
"zero affects both equally (isotropic)."
msgstr ""
"ທິດທາງຂອງຄວາມໄວລຳດັບທີ 1 (ຕັ້ງຄ່າດ້ານເທິງ).\n"
"\n"
"ຄ່າລົບຈະເນັ້ນຕາມເສັ້ນລະດັບຄວາມເຂັ້ມແສງ,\n"
"ຄ່າບວກຈະຫຼີກລ່ຽງຂອບຮູບ (isophotes),\n"
"ຄ່າສູນຈະສົ່ງຜົນຕໍ່ທັງສອງເທົ່າກັນ (isotropic)."

