msgstr "ເປີດ/ປິດ ໂໝດຖ່າຍຄູ່ຂະໜານ (bracketed)"

#: ../src/libs/camera.c:487
msgid "the count of seconds before actually doing a capture"
msgstr "ຈຳນວນວິນາທີກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເລີ່ມຖ່າຍພາບ"

#: ../src/libs/camera.c:489
msgid ""
"the amount of images to capture in a sequence,\n"
"you can use this in conjunction with delayed mode to create stop-motion sequences"
msgstr ""
"ຈຳນວນຮູບພາບທີ່ຈະຖ່າຍແບບຕໍ່ເນື່ອງ,\n"
